EventItemActionText: This Resolution was Referred to Comm by Council to the Committee on Consumer Affairs
EventItemTitle: Resolution calling upon President Bush to continue utilizing the Strategic Petroleum Reserve to mitigate the rising price of fuel caused by Hurricanes Katrina and Rita, and to compel him to consider alternative methods to help alleviate the concern over possible record-high winter fuel costs.
EventItemMatterName: Calling upon President Bush to continue utilizing the Strategic Petroleum Reserve.

EventItemActionText: This Resolution was Referred to Comm by Council to the Committee on Consumer Affairs

EventItemMatterName: Protect consumers from price gouging and for the NYS Attorney General to vigilantly continue investigating instances of potential price gouging.
